BungieNet.Engine.Contract.Destiny.World..subtitle: Cryptarch
BungieNet.Engine.Contract.Destiny.World..name: Master Rahool
BungieNet.Engine.Contract.Destiny.World..description: A senior representative of the Cryptarchy, Master Rahool decodes engrams and seeks the treasures of humanity's past.

overlay.title: Decode Engram
overlay.description: Each engram decoded sheds light on lost history.

interactions.flavorLineOne: Rahool frowns at the engram-shaped chunk of rock, but he chuckles after a second. It's clear he appreciates the jab.

"Fascinating! I haven't seen a design such as this in... hmm. There are Golden Age markers to this weapon that bear further research. If we're going to develop this line of thinking further, I will need fodder for my research. Engrams, to put it succinctly." —Cryptarch Rahool
interactions.instructions: "Fascinating! I haven't seen a design such as this in... hmm. There are Golden Age markers to this weapon that bear further research. If we're going to develop this line of thinking further, I will need fodder for my research. Engrams, to put it succinctly." —Cryptarch Rahool

interactions.flavorLineOne: "Interesting, Guardian. Very interesting. And marked with signatures from... hmm. In this case, I believe this to be beyond even my understanding. My colleague, Tyra Karn, may be able to set you on your path. Give her my regards. Won't you?" —Cryptarch Rahool

interactions.flavorLineOne: Rahool's mouth tightens at your approach, but he is polite enough as he accepts the gift.

In an effort to further the goals of the Cryptarchy, Master Rahool asks for your devotion. In exchange, he shares with you a Prime Engram, which decrypts to a piece of powerful gear.

Each day you will gain the Prime Attunement buff, which gives you a chance to find more Prime Engrams by defeating challenging enemies or completing Crucible matches.

"Well now, Guardian… Your Power increases, but I can see you're not done yet. There are more battles to be won… More lost frontiers to explore and more secrets to uncover."

Now, you can increase your Power level only by acquiring powerful gear. Continue to seek these treasures by completing challenges, decrypting Prime Engrams, and testing your might in pinnacle activities such as raids.

Keep pushing the limits of your strength, and you will continue to grow even more formidable.

"Part of every Guardian's journey is the path to unmatched Power. Seek out and equip more powerful gear to increase the limits of your strength, Guardian!"

Your Power level will increase as you equip your Guardian with more powerful gear.

Earn powerful gear and engage in activities with pinnacle rewards by completing the "Unlimited Power" quest offered by the Cryptarch.
A Cryptarch can decrypt complex engrams into powerful gear and other items.
